nodes.text: A male Trandoshan criminal was responsible for many atrocities against the Wookiee clan known as Strongfist. A wanted poster for him was created sometime during the Galactic Civil War, a series of conflicts between the Galactic Empire and the Alliance to Restore the Republic.

The Trandoshan criminal appeared in the 2003 MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies which was developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts. His appearance consisted of his picture being used for the aforementioned wanted poster and the poster's description indicating his crimes leading to the poster's creation.
